name: Selected prints - Various Sizes
description:
You will receive a selection of10 prints, ranging from analogue darkroom and digitally printed images from various projects over the years. 
From final images and test prints to some rare unseen photography work that I plan to put in. 

- Each print will be, named, signed, dated and stamped as a form of verification of it being an original. 

A range of different sizes of prints each priced fairly. 

Any other question please check the FAQs page, or get in contact.
